description: {"blocks":[{"key":"1cejb","text":"Immunohistochemistry is a method used to detect specific antigens in tissue sections. It exploits the principal of antibodies binding to specific antigens (epitopes). Visualisation of the target antigen is achieved by attaching an enzyme to the antibody-antigen conjugate and visualising it with (in this case) DAB chromogen.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"b0g4d","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"eim3t","text":"This SOP applies to FFPE tissue sections cut at 4µm. We use it almost exclusivley for human brain tissue however, it can work well for other tissue types. {"blocks":[{"key":"dvm26","text":"- Purpose:
The purpose of this SOP is to outline the correct procedures for performing Immunohistochemistry (IHC) using the Novolink Polymer Detection System kit. It is adapted from the Novolink Polymer Detection Systems instruction manual and is intended for the use by all staff, students, and users of the Gregory Laboratory.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ab6lm","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"90csc","text":"- Safety First:
Before starting, you must read all relevant Health & Safety documentation, and fully read this SOP. Please speak to any of the Gregory Lab technical staff if there is anything you are unsure about before embarking on your experiment, we are always happy to help.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"b8p7s","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d8ili","text":"COSHH and Risk assessments","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8np4h","text":"SOP","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9dnvr","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e4119","text":"- Special note:
